
/*
 * The code snippet adds nodes retrieved from the [.arguments] node to a specific location within a data structure. It uses [add] to insert nodes fetched by [get-nodes] from [.arguments] into the path specified by the expression in the [add] slot. This operation effectively merges nodes from [.arguments] into the target node set. 
 * 
 * 1. [add] - Inserts nodes into the specified path in the data structure.
 * 2. [get-nodes] - Retrieves nodes from the [.arguments] node to be added.
 */
